  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK287">
<l>kaḷaveṉṉuṅ kāraṟi vāṇmai yaḷaveṉṉu</l>
<l>māṟṟal purintārka ṇil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That black-knowledge which is called fraud, is not in those who desire that greatness which is called rectitude.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
